---
import "../styles/global.css";
import "flag-icons/css/flag-icons.min.css";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
import CountryLayout from "../components/CountryLayout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <meta
            name="description"
            content="Study MBBS in Europe – Comprehensive guide to medical education in Poland, Hungary, Romania, Bulgaria, and Italy for Indian students."
        />
        <title>Study MBBS in Europe: Top Universities, Fees & Admissions | Doctor Destiny</title>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-[#F0F7FF] overflow-x-hidden">
        <Navbar client:load />

        <!-- Page Hero -->
        <div class="bg-[#0E0C4F] pt-28 pb-16 px-6">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
                <span
                    class="inline-block py-1 px-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-[#D5AD36] text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                    Study Abroad
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-4"
                >
                    Study MBBS in <span class="text-[#00BFFF]">Europe</span>
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Europe is home to some of the world's oldest and most prestigious medical universities. Experience a high standard of living, world-class clinical training, and degrees recognized across the globe including Poland, Hungary, Romania, and Italy.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-8">
                    <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D5AD36] to-[#f0c847] hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(213,173,54,0.6)] text-[#0E0C4F] px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
                        Enroll Now
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Country Layout (3-column) -->
        <CountryLayout
            countryName="Europe"
            navItems={[
                { label: "Overview & Duration", id: "overview" },
                { label: "Top Destinations", id: "destinations" },
                { label: "Recognition", id: "recognition" },
                { label: "Eligibility", id: "eligibility" },
                { label: "Top Universities", id: "universities" },
                { label: "Why Europe?", id: "benefits" },
                { label: "Fee Structure", id: "fees" },
                { label: "Admission Process", id: "process" },
            ]}
            faqs={[
                {
                    question: "Is MBBS in Europe valid in India?",
                    answer: "Yes, many European medical universities are recognized by the NMC (National Medical Commission). Graduates can practice in India after passing the mandatory screening test (FMGE/NExT).",
                },
                {
                    question: "Do I need to learn the local language?",
                    answer: "While the degree is taught in English, learning the local language is often required or encouraged for communicating with patients during clinical rotations in the final years.",
                },
                {
                    question: "What is the duration of MBBS in Europe?",
                    answer: "The typical duration for an MBBS program in most European countries is 6 years, which includes both theoretical study and clinical practice.",
                },
                {
                    question: "Is NEET mandatory for studying in Europe?",
                    answer: "Yes, for Indian students to practice in India upon return, qualifying NEET is mandatory as per NMC guidelines.",
                }
            ]}
        >
            <!-- SECTION: Overview -->
            <section id="overview" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Overview & Course Duration
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 mb-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        Medical education in Europe is highly sought after for its adherence to ECTS (European Credit Transfer and Accumulation System) standards and its focus on clinical expertise. Countries like Poland, Hungary, and Romania have become major hubs for Indian students.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-3">
                        <span class="text-[#00BFFF]">⏱</span> Course Duration
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Overall duration: <strong>6 Years</strong>.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside">
                        <li><strong>Pre-Clinical Stage:</strong> Focus on anatomy, physiology, and biochemistry (Years 1-3).</li>
                        <li><strong>Clinical Stage:</strong> Practical training in hospitals and patient care (Years 4-6).</li>
                        <li><strong>Internship:</strong> Final years usually involve heavy clinical rotations.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Destinations -->
            <section id="destinations" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Main European Destinations
                </h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm">
                    <div class="bg-blue-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-pl"></span> Poland
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Known for high-tech medical simulation centers and strict academic standards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-red-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-red-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-hu"></span> Hungary
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Home to some of the top-ranked medical universities with centuries of history.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-yellow-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-yellow-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-ro"></span> Romania
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Affordable tuition fees and a large community of international medical students.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-indigo-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-it"></span> Italy
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Offers English-medium degrees through the IMAT entrance exam at public universities.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-emerald-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-emerald-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-bg"></span> Bulgaria
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Low living costs and modern facilities, gaining popularity among Indian students.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                           <span class="fi fi-by"></span> Belarus
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">A time-tested destination with extremely standardized medical curriculum.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Recognition -->
            <section id="recognition" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Global Recognition
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-[#0E0C4F] text-white p-6 rounded-2xl">
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-300">
                        European medical degrees are governed by the Bologna process and are globally recognized by:
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                        {
                            [
                                "World Health Organization (WHO)",
                                "National Medical Commission (NMC, India)",
                                "ECFMG (USA)",
                                "General Medical Council (GMC, UK)",
                                "FAIMER",
                                "UNESCO"
                            ].map((org) => (
                                <div class="bg-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm text-center font-medium border border-white/20">
                                    {org}
                                </div>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Eligibility -->
            <section id="eligibility" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Eligibility Criteria
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <span class="text-[#00BFFF] shrink-0 font-bold">50%</span>
                            <span>Minimum aggregate in Physics, Chemistry, and Biology (PCB) in 12th standard (40% for reserved categories).</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <span class="text-[#00BFFF] shrink-0 font-bold">NEET</span>
                            <span>Qualifying marks in NEET are mandatory for Indian students to practice in India.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <span class="text-[#00BFFF] shrink-0 font-bold">17+</span>
                            <span>Age must be at least 17 years by December 31st of the admission year.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <span class="text-[#00BFFF] shrink-0 font-bold">IELTS</span>
                            <span>Some top universities in Poland/Hungary may require basic English proficiency proof, though most don't.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Universities -->
            <section id="universities" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Top Universities in Europe
                </h2>
                <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                    <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse min-w-[600px]">
                        <thead>
                            <tr class="bg-[#0E0C4F] text-white text-sm">
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">University Name</th>
                                <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Country</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                            <tr class="border-b bg-white">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Semmelweis University</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Hungary</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50/50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Medical University of Warsaw</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Poland</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-white">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Jagiellonian University</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Poland</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50/50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">University of Debrecen</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Hungary</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-white">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Carol Davila University of Medicine</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Romania</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50/50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Medical University Sofia</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Bulgaria</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-white">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Humanitas University</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Italy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50/50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Charles University</td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">Czech Republic</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Benefits -->
            <section id="benefits" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Why Study MBBS in Europe?
                </h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm text-gray-700">
                    <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span>🇪🇺</span> EU Standards
                        </h4>
                        <p>High-quality clinical training that follows strict European Union guidelines and medical protocols.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span>🚂</span> Travel Benefits
                        </h4>
                        <p>Schengen visa allows students to travel across most European countries easily during holidays.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span>💼</span> Career Prospects
                        </h4>
                        <p>Strong base for taking residency exams like USMLE or PLAB due to world-class clinical foundations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span>🏫</span> Modern Infrastructure
                        </h4>
                        <p>Most universities feature digitalized libraries, simulation centers, and advanced laboratories.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION: Fees -->
            <section id="fees" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Fee Structure
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-blue-50/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100">
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Tuition fees in Europe vary significantly by country:</p>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                            <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-[#00BFFF] uppercase">Romania/Bulgaria</span>
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">€4,000 - €8,000 / Year</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                            <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-[#00BFFF] uppercase">Poland/Hungary</span>
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">€10,000 - €18,000 / Year</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                        *Note: Living expenses usually range between €300 - €600 per month depending on the city. 1 Euro (EUR) is approximately ₹88 - ₹92 INR.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

             <!-- SECTION: Process -->
            <section id="process" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-24">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0E0C4F] mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-[#00BFFF]/30">
                    Admission Process
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-5 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#0E0C4F] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Counselling</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Select the right country and university based on your budget and preferences with Doctor Destiny.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-5 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#0E0C4F] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Application</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Submission of documents (10th/12th marksheet, Passport copy, NEET scorecard).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-5 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#0E0C4F] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Admission Letter</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Upon approval, the university issues a provisional admission letter.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-5 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                        <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#D5AD36] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">4</span>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0E0C4F]">Visa & Travel</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Visa processing, document translation (if required), and pre-departure formalities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </CountryLayout>

        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
